  ('BP9', 'X-Guard Backstep Pass', 'blue', 'Passes', 55.0, 40.0, NULL, NULL, NULL, 15.0, NULL, NULL, 'GREEN if used value >= 15 (BOTH side) after age/injury modifiers; otherwise YELLOW or RED per TechniqueEligibility formulas. RISK: ER <50 → can''t clear hooks without knee torsion; simultaneous ER/IR split required. Confidence: MEDIUM'),
