  ('WG5', 'De La Riva Guard', 'white', 'Guards', 60.0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 15.0, NULL, NULL, 'GREEN if used value >= 15 after age/injury modifiers; otherwise YELLOW or RED per TechniqueEligibility formulas. RISK: <50° hip ER = Very High Risk (30+ avoid); <110° hip flex = knee torque risk'),
