  ('BS13', 'Dogfight to Single Leg', 'blue', 'Sweeps', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 20.0, NULL, NULL, 'GREEN if used value >= 20 (LEAD side) after age/injury modifiers; otherwise YELLOW or RED per TechniqueEligibility formulas. RISK: Same penetration step ROM as single-leg takedown; ankle DF <10 → can''t drive from kneeling-to-standing; lumbar ext <25 → front headlock vulnerability. Confidence: MEDIUM'),
