  ('BS16', 'Electric Chair Sweep (Lockdown)', 'blue', 'Sweeps', 55.0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 15.0, NULL, NULL, 'GREEN if used value >= 15 (BOTH side) after age/injury modifiers; otherwise YELLOW or RED per TechniqueEligibility formulas. RISK: Highest hip ext demand among sweeps; ER <50 → knee torsion; NOTE: forces opponent into extreme abduction — groin injury risk to opponent if they lack abd >55. Confidence: LOW. Flag: Missing lockdown biomechanics data.'),
