  ('WP4', 'Double Under Pass (Double Underhook Pass)', 'white', 'Passes', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'GREEN if used value >= 45 (midline, no laterality) after age/injury modifiers; otherwise YELLOW or RED per TechniqueEligibility formulas. RISK: <120° shoulder flex = Very High Risk; <30° spinal flex = DELAY for 30+ (cervical/lumbar disc injury risk)'),
